<title>Aircraft environmental control and refrigeration</title>
<description><h1 itemprop="title"> <a href="https://space.lib.buaa.edu.cn/space/searchDetailLocal/me7c9ce15a4211e09c7ec316717096c0e" style="color: #006fcc;">Aircraft environmental control and refrigeration </a> </h1> <aside><img src="https://img3m0.ddimg.cn/30/7/29652510-1_w_1700967818.jpg" alt="封面" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></aside> <h2>书籍信息</h2> <div> <span class="call-no" style="font-family: JetBrainsMono, monospace; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700; color: #458f57;">V245.3/E:06</span> / <span class="author">Xiande Fang = 飞行器环境控制和制冷技术 / 方贤德编著.</span> / <span class="publisher">Beihang University Press,</span> / <span class="pub-year">2023.</span> </div> <h3>简介</h3> <div itemprop="description">本书是高等学校来华留学生航空工程专业核心课程教材，本书较系统和较完整地阐述了飞行器环境控制系统的基本原理、基本组成以及基本设计和计算方法，以满足航空航天领域人才培养、科学研究和产品研制的需要。本书已经获得2021年江苏省重点教材立项建设，可作为相关专业工程技术人员有重要价值的参考书。</div> <table> <tbody><tr><th>ISBN</th><td itemprop="isbn">9787512440906</td></tr> <tr><th>语言</th><td itemprop="language">eng</td></tr> <tr><th>类型</th><td itemprop="docType">西文图书</td></tr> </tbody></table> <h3>作者简介</h3> <div itemprop="authorInfo"></div> <h2>馆藏信息</h2> <strong>上架时间</strong>： <date datetime="2024-07-24">2024-07-24</date> <br> <h3>馆藏地点</h3> <table> <tbody><tr><th>所属馆藏地</th><td>沙河校区-科研楼阅览室</td></tr> <tr><th>索书号</th><td>V245.3/E:06</td></tr> <tr><th>条码号</th><td>E2400623</td></tr> <tr><th>编号</th><td>3130719</td></tr> <tr> <th>书刊状态</th> <td style="color: #458f57">可借</td> </tr> </tbody></table> <h2>目录</h2> <div itemprop="catalog">Chapter 1 Introduction <br> 1.1 Scope and Background <br> 1.2 Functions of Aireraft Environmental Control <br> 1.2.1 nternal environmental control <br> 1.2.2 External protection <br> 1.3 Major Types of Aireraft Environmental Control Systems <br> 1.3.1 Air cycle <br> 1.3.2 Vapor cycle <br> 1.4 Development of Aireraft Environmental Control <br> 1.4.1 Occurrence of aireraft ECS <br> 1.4.2 Development of air cycle ECS <br> 1.4.3 Development of vapor cycle ECS <br> References <br> Review Questions and