4.2.1 Humidity ratio, d <br> 4.2.2 Saturation vapor pressure, Pw <br> …… <br>Chapter 5 Components of Environmental Control and Refrigeration <br>Chapter 6 Air Cycle Environmental Control Systems <br>Chapter 7 Design and Performance Calculation and Simulation of Air Cycle Systems <br>Chapter 8 Air Distribution System of Compartments <br>Chapter 9 Heating Systems <br>Chapter 10 Vapor Cycle Refrigeration Systems <br>Chapter 11 Flow Boiling Heat Transfer in Evaporators <br>Chapter 12 Condensation Heat Transfer in Condensers <br>Appendix <br></div> </description>
