<description><h1 itemprop="title"> <a href="https://space.lib.buaa.edu.cn/space/searchDetailLocal/m9a3468702e7d5426712742fb0cb14637" style="color: #006fcc;">研究生英语高阶教程</a> </h1> <aside><img src="https://img3m7.ddimg.cn/88/29/29667517-1_w_1703574930.jpg" alt="封面" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></aside> <h2>书籍信息</h2> <div> <span class="call-no" style="font-family: JetBrainsMono, monospace; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700; color: #458f57;">H319.39/290</span> / <span class="author">主编刘爽, 史光达</span> / <span class="publisher">北京航空航天大学出版社</span> / <span class="pub-year">2023</span> </div> <h3>简介</h3> <div itemprop="description">本书依据《非英语专业研究生英语教学大纲》的要求编写而成，编写上力求做到读写训练和文本特点相结合、阅读欣赏和写作训练相结合、文化底蕴与翻译训练相结合。全书分为八个单元，涉及新闻报道、传记、散文、科普文章、小说、诗歌、剧本及演讲词等多种体裁，内容涵盖医疗与健康、人工智能、文化艺术、婚姻与家庭、个人与自由、政界风云、商业挑战、科学技术等多种主题。每个单元都提供A、B两篇文章供学习选择，还配备了各种形式新颖、精心设计的练习题。本书将文献阅读、学术写作、中英文翻译等多种技巧相融合，培养学生对中外文化的认知与鉴赏能力。 本书选材大多来自国外网站或国内外书籍和报刊，内容新颖，语言地道，可供普通高等院校具有一定英语基础的本科生、硕士研究生和博士研究生作为教材使用，也可以作为大学英语课程和素质拓展课程的补充教材，还可供英语学习爱好者自学使用。</div> <table> <tbody><tr><th>ISBN</th><td itemprop="isbn">978-7-5124-4164-4</td></tr> <tr><th>语言</th><td itemprop="language">chi</td></tr> <tr><th>类型</th><td itemprop="docType">中文图书</td></tr> </tbody></table> <h3>作者简介</h3> <div itemprop="authorInfo"></div> <h2>馆藏信息</h2> <strong>上架时间</strong>： <date datetime="2024-07-22">2024-07-22</date> <br> <h3>馆藏地点</h3> <table> <tbody><tr><th>所属馆藏地</th><td>学院路校区-五层西-中文新书借阅室(A-Z类)</td></tr> <tr><th>索书号</th><td>H319.39/290</td></tr> <tr><th>条码号</th><td>C24042355</td></tr> <tr><th>编号</th><td>3128311</td></tr> <tr> <th>书刊状态</th> <td style="color: #458f57">可借</td> </tr> <tr><th>所属馆藏地</th><td>学院路校区-五层西-中文新书借阅室(A-Z类)</td></tr> <tr><th>索书号</th><td>H319.39/290</td></tr> <tr><th>条码号</th><td>C24042356</td></tr> <tr><th>编号</th><td>3128312</td></tr> <tr> <th>书刊状态</th> <td style="color: #458f57">可借</td> </tr> </tbody></table> <h2>目录</h2> <div itemprop="catalog">Unit One Health Care <br> Section A <br> The Dawn of Digital Medicine <br> Section B <br> How to Live Longer, Better <br> Writing Practice <br> Types of Writing <br>Unit Two Artificial Intelligence <br> Section A <br> Transforming Jobs in the Age of AI <br> Section B <br> The Magician Steve Jobs <br> Writing Practice <br> Exposition ~ Argumentation <br>Unit Three Cultural Arts <br> Section A <br> Why a Classic Is a Classic <br> Section B <br> Beauty <br> Writing Practice <br> Letter Writing <br>Unit Four Marriage Life <br> Section A <br> A More Perfect Union <br> Section B <br> The Gift of the Magi (Excerpt) <br> Writing Practice <br> Resume <br>Unit Five Freedom Pursuit <br> Section A <br> Those Rugged Individuals <br> Section B <br> The Road Not Taken <br> Writing Practice <br> Academic Writing <br>Unit Six Political World <br> Section A <br> The Corruption in Washington Is Smothering America's Future <br> Section B <br> President Barack Obama's Inaugural Address <br> Writing Practice <br> Abstract <br>Unit Seven Business Prosperity <br> Section A <br> What Happened the Last Time Hollywood Shut Down? <br> Section B <br> The Devil Wears Prada <br> Writing Practice <br> Summary Writing <br>Unit Eight Scientific Technology <br> Section A <br> New Directions—Map Making <br> Section B <br> Space Exploration <br> Writing Practice <br> Figure of Speech <br>Appendix <br> Key to Exercises <br> Reference Translation of the Texts <br>References <br></div> </description>
